    { "id": "rrule_t", "type": "text", "x": 990, "y": 175, "width": 250, "height": 200, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#075985", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "seed": 400081, "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "text": "规则负责\n计算与检索\n\n• 聚类/最近邻路径\n• prorate 预算分摊\n• 高德 POI/路线/天气\n• 精确核账", "containerId": "rrule", "updated": 1 },

