    { "id": "rgain", "type": "text", "x": 700, "y": 540, "width": 540, "height": 130, "angle": 0, "strokeColor": "#166534", "backgroundColor": "transparent", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100, "seed": 400110, "fontSize": 15, "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top", "text": "收益：\n• 任意城市 + 复杂偏好质量提升\n• special_notes 被真正理解\n• token 统计真实可观测\n• 编排层收敛为一套\n• 对外契约不变（TripRequest 进 / Itinerary 出）", "boundElements": null, "updated": 1 }
